  # Staff Check-In
  
  This endpoint allows staff members to check in for their shift.
  
  ## Response
  - Records check-in time
  - Sets status to PRESENT
  - Returns attendance record with staff info
  
  ## Business Rules
  - Only one check-in per day allowed
  - Must be authenticated staff member
  - Automatically sets isPresent to true
